text.tspan: Teal - #29E9E3 - Used for active icons, graph line & graph gradient
Blue 3 - #0D2437 - Used as divider lines color
Blue 4 - #091A29 - Used for scroll bar grip
Active - Teal icon, transparent binding box
W - varies depending on Search Bar width
Inactive - Blue 1 icon, transparent binding box
- Teal icon, White binding box, 10% opacity
H - depends on number of results
Always on if there are scrollable results
